<div style="max-width: 700px; margin: 40px auto; background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); padding: 36px;">
  <h1 style="color: #007bff; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 18px;">Wiki App</h1>
  <p style="font-size: 1.15em; color: #343a40; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px;">
    Welcome to the Wiki App! This is a simple application to create and manage wiki posts.
  </p>

  <h2 style="color: #28a745; margin-bottom: 12px;">Site Contributors</h2>
  <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 32px;">
    <% WikiPost.contributors.each do |contributor| %>
      <li style="background: #e9ecef; margin-bottom: 8px; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 6px; color: #495057; font-weight: 500;">
        <%= contributor.presence || "Anonymous" %>
      </li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>

  <h2 style="color: #17a2b8; margin-bottom: 12px;">About</h2>
  <p style="color: #444; margin-bottom: 10px;">
    This application allows users to create, edit, and view wiki posts. Each post has a title, author, and description. The posts are stored in a database and can be accessed through the application interface.
  </p>
  <p style="color: #444;">
    Feel free to explore the wiki posts and contribute by creating new posts!
  </p>
</div>